---
title: Spring Asparagus, Pea & Mint Penne with Ricotta
description: Spring is in the air! We're looking forward to warmer months with classic early-Spring ingredients like asparagus, mint and sweet peas! A dollop of creamy ricotta with a drizzle of olive oil is a luscious way to finish off this light  and bright pasta.
